"6  fresh poblano chiles (4 to 5 oz. each; see notes)","6 ounces bacon, cut crosswise into thin strips","12  large eggs","  About 1/2 teaspoon salt","  About 1/8 teaspoon pepper","1 1/2 cups shredded jack cheese (6 oz.)","1/3 cup thinly sliced chives or green onions","4  tomatoes (6 oz. each), rinsed, cored, and sliced 1/4 inch thick","2 tablespoons chopped fresh cilantro","  Crisp chile rings and oil (recipe follows; optional)"